Properties.DeveloperComment: Make the Weedkiller available in the basement

NPCDialogue.LocalizedString: GOOD WORK, MY BOY! BENDING SPACE AND TIME LIKE A CHAMP! @NOW, HAND ME THAT CRUSHROOM AND I'LL GET COOKING!
IF YOU THROW IT AT THE IRONWEED YOU'LL DISSOLVE IT IN A JIFFY... GIVE IT A GO! @OH... AND IF YOU WANT ANY MORE BOMBS I'LL LEAVE A FEW ON THE GROUND FLOOR OF MY HOUSE. @HAPPY GARDENING!
NICE OF YOU TO DROP BY, JOT!
MAGIC BARRIER SPELL - CHECK! THE SPELL OF RE-BINDING - ALL BOUND UP.
GRAND! WE'RE MAKING GOOD PROGRESS, VIOLET, MY GIRL!
GETTING THROUGH IT, YEP YEP! @... @AAAAAAANYWAY... @TO GET BACK TO WHAT WE WERE TALKING ABOUT... @SO... WE'RE CHARACTERS IN A BOOK... BUT THE PEOPLE OUTSIDE... LIKE SAM... @THEY'RE REALLY REAL?
AH. WE ARE BACK TO THIS, ARE WE? @WELL. @IT RATHER DEPENDS ON WHAT YOU MEAN BY REAL. I FEEL REAL ENOUGH. DON'T YOU?
WELL, THERE WE ARE THEN. @WE'RE REAL IN OUR OWN WAY. ALL THE PEOPLE OUTSIDE OUR WORLD ARE REAL IN THEIR WAY. @ALL... REALLY REAL.
D'YOU THINK... PEOPLE OUT THERE... CAN SEE US?
YEP! AND... I THINK I CAN JUST ABOUT MAKE THEM OUT, TOO...

Y'KNOW... I CAN SENSE THAT YOU OUT THERE ARE... SUPPORTING US... IN SOME WAY... @SO... THANK YOU FOR YOUR EFFORTS SO FAR! @LET'S ALL PUT OUR BEST FOOT FORWARD, SHALL WE? @WHICH MEANS... IN THIS REALITY...

HELLO AGAIN, JOT! @IF YOU'RE LOOKING FOR WEEDKILLER BOMBS, YOU'LL FIND THEM ON THE GROUND FLOOR! @UMMM... THE LAB'S A BIT OF A MESS AT THE MO... THE STAIRS ARE BLOCKED. @CAN'T BE BOTHERED TO CLEAN UP RIGHT NOW, I'M IN THE ZONE. @YOU'LL HAVE TO FIND ANOTHER WAY TO THE GROUND FLOOR, LAD!
NICE OF YOU TO DROP BY, JOT!

NPCDialogueSequence.LocalizedString: NICE OF YOU TO DROP BY, JOT!
